<h1>Pyrubi 2.1.1</h1>

> Pyrubi is a powerful and easy library for building self Bots in Rubika

<p align='center'>
    <img src='https://iili.io/HIjPRS9.jpg' alt='Pyrubi Library 2.1.1' width='356' class="image">
</p>

